    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "text": "Growing materials in the $(l:magical_blocks/crystallarieum)Crystallarieum$(/l) yields this much more pure, crystalline variant compared to plain $(thing)Raw Ore$().$(br)On closer inspection they almost appear surrounded by an invisible sheen, gently protecting them from outside forces. This shroud also seems to be what protects $(thing)Native Copper$() from oxidization."
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:blasting",
