      "recipe2": "spectrum:blasting/pure_resources/pure_gold",
      "text": "Ironically, you found that these resources seemed to be able to withstand the heat of normal $(thing)Furnaces$(). But you were able to smelt them in a $(thing)Blast Furnace$(), at least."
    },
